Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,The operator told me the GPS failed under a tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:11.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,Black Box checked the recording and said: that story is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:15.45,Cap,,0,0,0,,Robotics teams collect hours of video\, lidar\, telemetry\,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:18.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,and controller logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:24.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,The evidence exists\, but forensic review is still manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:30.45,Cap,,0,0,0,,One real driving session. No labels.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:35.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,Just the operator's note: check the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:37.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,Black Box opens it as a forensic case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:40.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,Not a one-shot summary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:43.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,Opus 4.7 runs as a managed forensic agent —
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:47.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,reading files\, calling tools\, streaming events.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:54.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,Memory carries forward across runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:57.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,It doesn't send every frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:02.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,Telemetry selects suspicious windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:09.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,High-resolution visual mining checks the relevant cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:13.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,The tunnel did mildly degrade GNSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:17.45,Cap,,0,0,0,,But the RTK heading failure was already present
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:20.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,43 minutes earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:24.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,Drive-by-wire was never engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:30.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,The tunnel could not have caused this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:34.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,Operator hypothesis: refuted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:38.45,Cap,,0,0,0,,The real failure is lower level.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:41.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,Moving-base antenna: healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:46.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,Rover: never receives valid RTK heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:54.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,The correction path was broken before the car left the lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:57.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,The output isn't just a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:02:01.45,Cap,,0,0,0,,Scoped patch: RTCM IDs\, UART link check\,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:06.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,and a human-review gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,Black Box proposes. Engineer approves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:13.45,Cap,,0,0,0,,Same benchmark slice. Opus 4.6 vs 4.7.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:16.45,Cap,,0,0,0,,Same cases\, same prompts\, same budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:19.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,On simple post-mortems they tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:23.45,Cap,,0,0,0,,But robot forensics punishes confident wrong answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:26.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,4.6 committed on every under-specified case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:29.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,4.7 abstained every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:34.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,Not a single-car demo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:38.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,More car sessions. A robotic boat case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:42.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,Clean recordings and injected benchmark failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:46.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,When evidence is weak\, it refuses to invent a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:50.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,No evidence. No claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,Open benchmark. Reproducible runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.95,Cap,,0,0,0,,Robot forensics in minutes\, for cents.
